sinks.name: Sink1
sinks.script:
sink(input(
		CountryID as string,
		Country as string,
		Category as string,
		CountryName as string,
		Waves as string,
		TotalTime as string,
		Environment as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Sink1
